      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. Applicant must be registered with the State Social Security Board at least 90 days in advance.\n1. Applicant must be in the age group of 18 to 60 years will be eligible for this scheme.\n1. Applicant can be only received benefits at once. \n1. If applicant received from any other parallel scheme of the State Government, then he/she is not eligible for this scheme.\n\n",
